data.meta_description:
149 likes, 2 comments - acchampionship on May 17, 2024: "Congrats to the Boston Celtics for making it to the eastern conference finals - will they play the Knicks or Pacers? Which teams do you think will be in the NBA Finals? Former Boston Celtic and Hall of Famer, Ray Allen, will return to the #ACCGolf field of sports and entertainment superstars along with ESPN College Basketball Analyst, Jay Bilas. Other NBA stars previously announced include: Charles Barkley, Austin Reaves, Blake Griffin, Dell Curry, Seth Curry, Kyle Lowry and Vinny Del Negro.
.
.
.
#nbaplayoffs2024 #NBA @celtics @nba @nbcsports @acchampionship @edgewoodtahoe @visitlaketahoe_official".
